# wharfkit-godot local configuration template.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in machine-specific values:
#
#   cp .env.example .env
#   $EDITOR .env
#
# `.env` is gitignored. Scripts (scripts/ios-deploy.sh) and the Makefile
# source it automatically when present. Anything settable here can also be
# overridden by exporting the env var directly in your shell.

# iOS device deploy (scripts/ios-deploy.sh). Both required for that script.
#
# Find IOS_DEVICE_BUILD_ID:
#   Xcode → Window → Devices and Simulators → select device → Identifier
# Find IOS_DEVICE_CTL_ID:
#   xcrun devicectl list devices
IOS_DEVICE_BUILD_ID=
IOS_DEVICE_CTL_ID=

# App bundle id. Must match the provisioning profile installed on the device.
IOS_BUNDLE_ID=com.wharfkit.example

# Xcode build configuration (Debug or Release).
IOS_CONFIG=Debug

# Godot export preset name (defined in example/export_presets.cfg).
IOS_PRESET=iOS-device

# Godot binary location. Default works for standard macOS installs.
GODOT_BIN=/Applications/Godot.app/Contents/MacOS/Godot
